short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Identify the nft rank all at once!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a quick tool that builds on top of JPG.store where users get to see the rank of all the items in the CNFT marketplace without browsing through other rarity website. Rarity rank plays an important factor in any NFT purchase hence with this extension installed, users get to enjoy a simpler and more effective shopping experience in CNFT marketplace
